#: ../../../lib/web/src/components/restore-banner.tsx:82
msgid "Your account was moved here from {source}. Until you delete it there, messages and notifications may reach both servers, some of your content keeps being served from the old server, and followers may take a few minutes to find you here."
msgstr "Jou rekening is hierheen geskuif vanaf {source}. Totdat jy dit daar uitvee, kan boodskappe en kennisgewings albei bedieners bereik, word sommige van jou inhoud steeds vanaf die ou bediener bedien, en kan volgelinge 'n paar minute neem om jou hier te vind."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:116
msgid "Your account will be permanently deleted on {purgeDate}. You've been signed out. To cancel, sign in again before then."
msgstr "Jou rekening sal permanent verwyder word op {purgeDate}. Jy is afgemeld. Om te kanselleer, meld weer aan voor dan."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:84
msgid "Your account will be scheduled for deletion and you'll be signed out. You can cancel any time before the deletion date by logging back in. Download your data first if you want to keep a copy."
msgstr "Jou rekening sal vir verwydering geskeduleer word en jy sal afgemeld word. Jy kan enige tyd voor die verwyderingsdatum kanselleer deur weer aan te meld. Laai eers jou data af as jy 'n kopie wil hou."

#: src/features/user/replication.tsx:200
msgid "Your account's data on this server will be permanently deleted and you'll be signed out here. Your account stays on your other servers, and you can re-add this one later."
msgstr "Jou rekening se data op hierdie bediener sal permanent geskrap word en jy sal hier afgemeld word. Jou rekening bly op jou ander bedieners, en jy kan hierdie een later weer byvoeg."

